data.description: Beautiful, spacious 5 (yes, FIVE) bedroom home on a greenbelt in a popular community on the far west-side. Convenient to shopping, services, Lackland, theme parks and downtown. Well maintained and some of the upgrades include; solar panels, reverse osmosis, water softener, additional patio and driveway, and a mini-split a/c in the garage for your workshop. A secondary bedroom and full bath down for guests or a family member and granite, a second floor balcony, and spacious closets and bedrooms really make this home stand out.
